  "subject": "Change Liquibase to use session lock",
  "commit_message": "Change Liquibase to use session lock\n\nAdd liquibase-sessionlock dependency so that locks will be\nautomatically released on failure, e.g. DB disconnection\nwhile Liquibase is running.\n\nIssue-ID: POLICY-5526\nChange-Id: I8f302b2fc3ef5d5c935e8bfd054faf7890f7deb9\nSigned-off-by: danielhanrahan <daniel.hanrahan@est.tech>\n",
